UML:TaggedValue.value:
All fixed (whether temporary or permanent) and mobile objects, or parts thereof that extend above the surface of the Earth. Those vertical structures, referred to as obstacles, that extend above a defined surface intended to protect aircraft in flight.
Name: (from Unit Definition): The name of the vertical obstruction. This item should be populated where name is known.
Description (from Unit Definition): The description of the type of Vertical Obstruction feature, for example 'aerial', 'wind turbine generator', 'chimney'.
